QUESTION 3:
Imagine you are building a personal portfolio website. Design a web page layout that
includes a header, a navigation menu, a main content area for displaying your projects
and a footer. Explain how you would structure the HTML code and apply CSS styles to
achieve the desired layout and visual design.

ANSWER:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Lakshana's Portfolio</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset default spacing */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    /* Body and layout */
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      color: #333;
    }

    /* Header */
    header {
      background-color: #333;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 30px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* Navigation */
    nav {
      background-color: #444;
    }

    nav ul {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      list-style: none;
    }

    nav ul li {
      margin: 10px 20px;
    }

    nav ul li a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    nav ul li a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* Main content */
    main {
      padding: 40px;
    }

    section#projects {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    .project-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .project-card h3 {
      color: #007acc;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      background-color: #222;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Header -->
  <header>
    <h1>Lakshana S</h1>
    <p>B.Sc. CS | Web Developer | Coder </p>
  </header>

  <!-- Navigation Menu -->
  <nav>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#about">About Me</a></li>
      <li><a href="#projects">Projects</a></li>
      <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <!-- Main Content Area -->
  <main>
    <section id="projects">
      <h2>My Projects</h2>

      <div class="project-card">
        <h3>WriteMate AR</h3>
        <p>An AR app to help children with learning disabilities improve handwriting using animated letter tracing and voice guidance.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card">
        <h3>EchoBoard</h3>
        <p>An AI-powered real-time meeting summarizer and visualizer using AR and accessibility tools.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card">
        <h3>Own website eco friendly</h3>
        <p>I personally created a own website for eco-friendly and eco-friendly products to buy</p>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card">
        <h3>DBMS </h3>
        <p>Airlines management system</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Add more project cards as needed -->

    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Lakshana S | All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>

